This extension is a companion for the Synology DS Manager MacOS application so, you need to install one first.

Synology DS Manager is the macOS application for your Synology Download Station.
It allows you to manage the Download Station tasks right from your Mac.

Features supported:
- your Synology Download Station connection credentials are securely stored in macOS keychain;
- 2-step authentication (2FA) support;
- embedded Chrome/Safari extension allows you to add new downloads right from your browser;
- select any shared folder as the download destination;
- hide Dock icon option;
- simultaneously specify up to multiple torrent-files and/or direct download URLs at Add Download step;
- search for new torrents right from the application!
